Description: Provides an R interface to PJRT (Pretty much Just another
    RunTime), which allows you to run XLA or stableHLO programs on a
    variety of hardware backends including CPU, GPU, and TPU.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://r-xla.github.io/pjrt/, https://github.com/r-xla/pjrt
